        <p class="printer-facts-heading">Drive Your Hashtag Further</p>
        <p class="printer-facts-body">Incentivize consumers to tag their photos with your brand or event hashtag, driving viral reach.</p>
        
        <p class="printer-facts-heading">Engage Via Offers & Competitions</p>
        <p class="printer-facts-body">Integrate hashtag competitions or brand your printed photos with exclusive offers to engage consumers further.</p>
        
